'''Uǧana''' (Tafransist: Oujana, Taɛrabt: أوجانة), d yiwet taɣiwant n Tmurt Leqbayel, i tezga-d al 30 km g anẓul n Tawilayt n Jijel. Taɣiwant-aya, tesɛa azal n 9 580 deg useggas n 2008. Di lweqt n listiɛmar llan qqarn-as ''zemmouren'', Imezdaɣ-ines mazal ihadren Tamaziɣt (Tasaḥlit) lwaḥi d Taɛrabt (Taǧiǧlit).
